{"tid":2170113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Pompeo出訪以色列和阿聯酋傳將討論伊朗、中國威脅","createTime":"2020-08-23T04:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T02:06:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8fd47ba82a2d40b4936b0d17956c2c7a0609944","tid":2170113,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）24日起將前往以色列和阿拉伯聯合大公國（阿聯），討論兩國關係正常化。據消息人士透露，伊朗和中國對中東地區構成的安全威脅也在此次的議程上，顯示出美國拉攏盟邦，形成圍堵的戰略意圖。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，在美國的斡旋下，以色列和阿聯8月13日宣布雙邊關係正常化<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n該協議也將團結反伊朗陣營的力量，美國、以色列和阿聯皆視伊朗為中東地區的最大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n在此背景下，龐皮歐24日將前往以色列，隔日再前往阿聯，討論兩國關係正常化。根據不願透露姓名和國籍的消息人士透露，龐皮歐此次的議程還包含伊朗和中國對中東構成的安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3268770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3268770&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=40b64057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3268770&h=9d0cdd7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3268770</a>"},{"pid":"a0963566b14eaf2529ec3d20f03c8a8254fee0fe","tid":2170113,"uid":254383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"呢輪成日飛好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66f6557ee72d5b788f6bef5a573d99f7d781f58","tid":2170113,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"打中東戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bd9801f5b9924d409d4a849f67de91e5fa5681","tid":2170113,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"UAE支持國